List of all the pre-defined MEMC models

memc_all_configs.Rd

List of all the pre-defined MEMC models

Usage

memc_all_configs

Format

A easy-to-iterate-over list, each element of which is one of the MEMC models.

See also

MEND_config, COMISSION_config, CORPSE_config, MEMS_config, BAMS_config, MIMCS_config

Examples

memc_all_configs
#> $MEND
#> $name
#> [1] "MEND"
#> 
#> $table
#>   model DOMuptake POMdecomp MBdecay
